quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  21,82,"Wamina ashshayateeni manyaghoosoona lahu wayaAAmaloona AAamalan doona thalikawakunna lahum hafitheen"
  21,83,"Waayyooba ith nadarabbahu annee massaniya addurru waanta arhamuarrahimeen"
  21,84,"Fastajabna lahu fakashafnama bihi min durrin waataynahu ahlahuwamithlahum maAAahum rahmatan min AAindina wathikralilAAabideen"
  21,85,"Wa-ismaAAeela wa-idreesa wathaalkifli kullun mina assabireen"
  21,86,"Waadkhalnahum fee rahmatinainnahum mina assaliheen"
  21,87,"Watha annooni ith thahabamughadiban fathanna an lan naqdira AAalayhifanada fee aththulumatian la ilaha illa anta subhanaka inneekuntu mina aththalimeen"
  21,88,"Fastajabna lahu wanajjaynahumina alghammi wakathalika nunjee almu/mineen"
  21,89,"Wazakariyya ith nadarabbahu rabbi la tatharnee fardan waanta khayru alwaritheen"
  21,90,"Fastajabna lahu wawahabnalahu yahya waaslahna lahuzawjahu innahum kanoo yusariAAoona fee alkhayratiwayadAAoonana raghaban warahaban wakanoo lanakhashiAAeen"
